* &quot;Spaceballs&quot; - a sci-fi comedy film that parodies Star Wars and other sci-fi franchises
* &quot;Redshirts&quot; - a novel that satirizes Star Trek tropes, particularly the fate of low-ranking crew members
* List of cult films

